Class: Chart

insight. Chart

new insight.Chart(name, element)

The Chart class is the element in which series and axes are drawn
Name Type Description
name String A uniquely identifying name for this chart
element String The css selector identifying the div container that the chart will be drawn in.
Example
 var myChart = new insight.Chart('My Chart', '#chart-div');

Methods
